Vladimir Nabokov





TO: THE INTERNATIONAL HERALD TRIBUNE

CC, 1 p.





57, Promenade des Anglais

Nice (A.M.)

Feb. 25, 1961

Sir,

I am about to start a devastating war against genteel mistranslators. This, however, is an incidental foray.